1. "Vidim da ideš u pravcu *kuda*." (I see that you are going in the direction.)
2. "Ona se kreće u istom *kudu*, kao i mi." (She is moving in the same direction as us.)
3. "Svi idu u *kudu* koju je on odredio." (Everyone is going in the direction he determined.)
4. "Ko *kuda* je otišao?" (Which direction did he go?)
5. "Moraš da znaš *kuda* idemo." (You have to know which direction we are going.)
6. "Čujem da je *kuda* otišao u nepoznato." (I hear he went in an unknown direction.)